1. The red fruit hanging from the tree was a crisp apple.
2. She took a big bite out of the juicy apple.
3. He dropped the shiny apple into the basket.
4. The teacher gave each student a small green apple.
5. My favorite snack is always a fresh apple.
6. The pie filling was made from sliced apples.
7. A worm was hiding inside the rotten apple.
8. The idiom "the apple of my eye" describes someone very dear.
9. The logo on the computer screen is a bitten apple.
10. The farmer sold every single apple at the market. [end of text]


